{
  "stem": "7337.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, Paris is a city of culture, and there's so much to-- to learn and to see that you can't do it, literally, in a lifetime in any depth.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And my father found a German-Jewish lawyer who was an illegal immigrant-- couldn't get a carte d'identite-- and who was absolutely penniless.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But he was a very proud man, and he wouldn't accept any help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my dad asked him whether he would take me on Sundays, on the weekends when I was off, and take me through French museums.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this he-- he accepted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he accepted money for that, and that was one way that my father could at least provide him with some small income.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And those museum visits, which were prepared by him in historical sequence, whatever I know today on-- of art or of culture, that's how I learned it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was invaluable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Unfortunately, this man was-- disappeared during the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We could never find him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I presume he was taken back to Germany and to one of the camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We were not able to find him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The Red Cross couldn't find him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Of course, we were here by then, and we had to search for him from here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so there was a small German-Jewish [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] crowd of immigrants.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my father was occupied with helping them and organizing them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, you had to find places for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
